page.title: 10HIGH BEECHES
page.content: High Beeches is a very romantic garden.There are lovely views and it has five ponds.Many species of rhododendrons and azaleas are grown.They have very bright colours.The owner said that they are preserving rare plants such as wild orchids.There are some ducks and a goose.There is a picnic site for visitors. There are some very old stable buildings which are not safe.It is open to the public in the Spring in the Summer and in the Autumn when the leaves are changing colour.They have 30 acres of land which they own.They own one meadow which is full of wild flowers.
